<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ pageTitle }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .restaurant-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content .details {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .details .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>{{ restaurant.name }} Reservation Confirmation</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{ guest.name }},</p>
            <p>We are pleased to confirm your reservation at <strong>{{ restaurant.name }}</strong>.</p>

            <div class="details">
                <p><span class="label">Reservation Date:</span> {{ reservationDate }}</p>
                <p><span class="label">Reservation Time:</span> {{ reservationTime }}</p>
                <p><span class="label">Number of Persons:</span> {{ reseervationNumberOfPersons }}</p>
            </div>

            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us or visit our website for more information.</p>
            <p>We look forward to welcoming you!</p>

            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p><strong>{{ restaurant.name }}</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>For any inquiries, please contact us at <a href="mailto:{{ restaurant.email }}">{{ restaurant.email }}</a></p>
            {# <p><a href="{{ url('guest_cancel_reservation', {
                'reservationId': reservation.id,
                'id': restaurant.id,
                'token': token,
            }) }}"
            target="_blank">You can cancel your reservation by visiting this link</a></p> #}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
